Command line Facebook status update bot v1.0

SYSTEM PREREQUISITES
-unix like OS (works also on Mac OS X;)
-curl

INSTRUCTIONS
-appy permissions: chmod +x ./fb.sh
-open fb.sh and edit email and password fields
-run it

